[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Crime Recording in Kent (2013)[bold]1.
[normal]6
[normal] In
[normal] February 2013, the Pol
[normal]ice and 
[normal]Crime Commissioner for Kent co
[normal]mmissioned HMIC to conduct an inspection to determine whether the people of Kent can have confidence in the force’s crime figures. 
