[normal]ed
[normal] to be done before the people of Kent c
[normal]ould
[normal] be confident that the crime and resolution figures published by the force 
[normal]we
[normal]re 
[normal]as accurate as they should be. HMIC found that the force had under-recorded approximately one in every ten crimes
[normal],
[normal] and that 
[normal]it
[normal] d
[normal]id
[normal] not interpret the Home Office Counting Rules (HOCR) correctly, 
[normal]meaning
[normal] crimes 
[normal]we
[normal]re not correctly recorded
[normal]. 
[normal]I
