[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]2.1 None of HMIC
[normal]’s
[normal] re
[normal]views of crime data integrity 
[normal]has
[normal] 
[normal]specifically 
[normal]examined
[normal] the influences which may lead to the mis-recording of crime
[normal] by the police
